ourself somewhere new. There''s a whole world out there.', 15081, 0), (70764, 'If we are what we repeatedly do, how many times did you express gratitude today? Showing that you''re grateful is the only way to be a grateful human being. Saying the words is not enough; you have demonstrate it through deeds.', 3620, 0), (70765, 'He never looked back, the day he realized the power of presentations.', 14751, 0), (70766, 'At the end of the day we’re all reactive personalities. We just don’t know it until we meet the right catalyst.', 15082, 0), (70767, 'It''s not just the thought we think that matter; it''s how we think them, how long we think them, and how often we think them. A thought has to be thought again and again in order for it to embed in our brains. So to fade a thought or get rid of it altogether, stop thinking it.', 3620, 0), (70768, 'INTROSPECT. Dive deep into your own Life and think...Think..."How have I lived ?" "How can I make my Life better?" -RVM', 5635, 0), (70769, 'The origin of the word fail means to stop functioning. So as long as you haven''t stopped, you haven''t failed.', 3620, 0), (70770, 'There are just two ways in life..either you do it or you don''t!!', 15083, 0), (70771, 'No one creates a perfect resume on their first try.', 11741, 0), (70772, 'Success demands a price that only a few are willing to pay ... blood, flesh, time, money, pride, heartbreak and energy. Anyone who has ever succeeded has the battle scars to prove the sacrifices they''ve made.', 3620, 0), (70773, 'Happiness is not something you pursue, it is a state of mind and a feeling of positivity, within.', 10924, 0), (70774, 'Contentment is the foundation of true Happiness. The Happiness that comes from fulfilling desires can never be permanent.-RVM', 5635, 0), (70775, 'Selling is a sacred trust between buyer and seller.', 1509, 0), (70776, 'Nothing worth doing''s ever easy.', 15084, 0), (70777, 'Everyone will grow older, but few will grow wiser.', 15085, 0), (70778, 'People lose their way when they lose their why.', 15086, 0), (70779, '[WASHINGTON]It’s alright, you want to fight, you’ve got a hungerI was just like you when I was youngerHead full of fantasies of dyin’ like a martyr?[HAMILTON]Yes[WASHINGTON]Dying is easy, young man. Living is harder', 1844, 0), (70780, 'To evade arrogance, remind yourself (from time to time) that your talent or success could have been better. To be thankful, remind yourself (every now and then) that your illness or failure could have been worse.', 4616, 0), (70781, 'Your life looks like a prison because you focus on the things you wish you had and thus don’t appreciate what you already have.So why don’t you try to see the abundance in your life? Because, if you haven’t noticed, you’ve got many things to thank for. Just look around.', 15087, 0), (70782, 'Rationality and calm self-determination were one of the great illusions of the universe... in the end, we were all ruled by our passions.', 9446, 0), (70783, 'If only you knew how beautiful you are unconditionally. Don''t you know it''s enough if all you do is breathe?', 5684, 0), (70784, 'Depression is state of deep anxiety. It is better to pray about everything than worry about nothing.', 2878, 0), (70785, 'Only a writer "with Bennett''s craft and brass could manage to praise and insult his readers at the same time.', 11750, 0), (70786, 'New thinking doesn''t mean shuffling your old thoughts around; it means getting rid of the old and implementing the new. That way your, "I can''t" become "I can!" and "I did!', 3620, 0), (70787, 'While JFK had made the sale on a political level, he had not yet completed it on an emotional one.', 15088, 0), (70788, 'Believe in your sacred self: strength of your being.', 2878, 0), (70789, 'May the Lord deliver us from every danger.', 2878, 0), (70790, 'Would we not do well to have the pleasing of God as our motive rather than to try to elevate ourselves above our brother and outdo another?', 1826, 0), (70791, 'House Speaker 