ime is not so important for me, the person asking for commitment is.', 15156, 0), (71182, 'Do couples in arranged marriage actually fall in love ', 15157, 0), (71183, 'We gradually accepted each other with our strengths and weaknesses. And now, I think, we have started to enjoy our differences more', 15156, 0), (71184, 'You may wonder why so many of my quotes - and all my work - is about love, compassion and inner peace? Because life is nothing, empty, bereft without these things.', 4889, 0), (71185, 'Icarus should have waited for nightfall,the moon would have never let him go.', 15158, 0), (71186, 'Van Gogh couldn''t have painted the stars in your eyes.', 15158, 0), (71187, 'I have feelings from my soul that sometimes supersedes my humanness.', 15159, 0), (71188, 'Maturity is not when we start speaking big things.It is when we start understanding the small things ....... @R$H', 15160, 0), (71189, 'Your tenderness has pervaded into the very pore of my being. Last night I inhaled the fragrance of the moon!', 5535, 0), (71190, 'Love rains against backcloth of unconditional emotion which washes away even pinch of hatred.', 5579, 0), (71191, 'We were just two broken souls trying to fix one another...Somehow I ended up with a piece of you and you me', 4545, 0), (71192, 'Truth has the biggest mouth in the universe, wisdom has the largest ears, love has the strongest hands, and faith has the ablest feet.', 5104, 0), (71193, 'Telling people Jesus loves them is a lie if you are not showing them!', 3801, 0), (71194, 'Let me show you how beautiful life is,Let me take away all your pain;Let me rekindle your faith in love,Let me make you believe in magic again!', 5149, 0), (71195, 'Last night I inhaled the fragrance of the Moon!', 5535, 0), (71196, 'Margaret had often wondered at the disturbance that takes place in the world''s waters when Love, who seems so tiny a pebble, slips in. Whom does Love concern beyond the beloved and the lover? Yet his impact deluges a hundred shores,