anted to do something, make a move and let our impulses take over, we put them neatly one behind other and now it comes crashing down around us.', 14664, 0), (71314, 'I wanted to leave marks or what?prints or blemishes? so when they track you, they''d know, i''d been there inside you, like an odour of your skin', 15172, 0), (71315, 'Love is the heart of a heart', 2760, 0), (71316, 'Don’t Waste your time I won’t be around Your heart For so long …………….Baby don’t Wait for me Tonight I’ll be in another town Looking for love ………………….', 15150, 0), (71317, 'You will love and admire the One who is honest and blunt in his views, as long as you''re not his subject of viewpoint!', 12721, 0), (71318, 'I waited for so long To let you know What I feel For you You’re my endless dream ……..', 15150, 0), (71319, 'Like petals what''s beautiful is often delicate. Take care of the ones you love by not holding them too tightly', 8393, 0), (71320, 'I know a feeling like that only comes once in a lifetime, and I think you should follow your heart’s desires. I believe in love, and I know love conquers all.', 15173, 0), (71321, 'If we all die and become stars then I must believe that our souls live in the stars. Now I know why people look up to the sky when they think of someone they wish to see', 8393, 0), (71322, 'Remember when we told each other no distractions?Yes. He runs a blazing finger over my earrings, touching each one in turn.Distract me.', 3246, 0), (71323, 'a man cannot hate unless he hates himself. Likewise one can only love another if they love themselves.', 10817, 0), (71324, 'When she needs you, she knows how to find you, but when you need her, she’s too busy to be with you.', 15150, 0), (71325, 'I am a lover of words and tragically beautiful things, poor timing and longing, and all things with soul, and I wonder if that means I am entirely broken, or if those are the things that have been keeping me whole.', 6343, 0), (71326, 'I miss talking to her and talking to her used to make me feel alive', 15150, 0), (71327, 'I’ve noticed that once you find the right one for you, the one of your dreams, everything in life becomes against you, even the weather', 15150, 0), (71328, 'Close your eyes for a whileThe image that conjures is your soulmate Don’t pause, rush and say what you feelAfter all time and tide for none wait…', 5095, 0), (71329, 'Maybe that was what being together with someone really meant. It meant seeing past the idealization you had of them, embracing their flaws and fears, helping them to overcome them, waiting for them if they were not ready. Maybe being in love didn’t mean finding the perfect person, it meant it was worth sticking with an imperfect one.', 15174, 0), (71330, 'Maybe a combination of things in this world are our true soul mates.', 5098, 0), (71331, 'What your father never understood, is that what he loved most about her was her unbridled love and freedom to live her own life. He loved her colors and viewed her like paint.', 10817, 0), (71332, 'You will not know love if you do not know suffering, and you will never suffer if you have never loved.', 10817, 0), (71333, 'When you get to find love, make sure it''s because you get to find yourself', 8393, 0), (71334, 'Your heart beats between the palm of my hand.Its need to beOne with meDripsBetween my fingertipsAs I squeeze perfect drops of love into small receptacles to be preserved...For later. ☕️', 7585, 0), (71335, 'You give me the duty to write about love', 8393, 0), (71336, 'People just don’t get it, we don’t need someone to control our life, we need someone to share it, relationships are falling apart cause they keep digging in our past , they don’t wanna let it Rest In Peace', 15150, 0), (71337, 'This world needs much more kissing and far less fighting.', 5027, 0), (71338, 'You know that you love someone when they are on your mind from the time you awake until the time you fall asleep. That you loved them yesterday as much as you do today and more tomorrow.'